          "label": "1 Kommando\u2019s slugga and choppa can be replaced with 1 burna and 1 close combat weapon.",
          "items": []
        },
        {
          "type": "option_group",
          "label": "1 Kommando\u2019s slugga and choppa can be replaced with 1 rokkit launcha and 1 close combat weapon.",
          "items": []
        },
        {
          "type": "option_group",
          "label": "This unit can be equipped with 1 bomb squig.",
          "items": []
        },
        {
          "type": "option_group",
          "label": "This unit can be equipped with 1 distraction grot.",
          "items": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "PATROL SQUAD",
      "entries": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "At the start of the Declare Battle Formations step this unit can be split into two units, each containing five models. (when splitting a unit in this way, make a note of which models form each of the two new units. If you are splitting a unit that is equipped with 1 bomb squig and/or 1 distraction grot, only one of the new units can use that ability during the battle \u2013 make a note of which of the new units this will be)."
        }
      ]
    },
